cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with automatic segmentation of medical images using deep learning techniques, specifically Conditional Adversarial Networks and Fully Convolutional Networks. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of deep learning models for medical image analysis is a popular area of research in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the proposed method involves optimization using a loss function, which is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
